{
  "texts": [
    "Table 1 presents detailed information on the sizes of all the datasets curated and used in our experiments.",
    "For all three models and datasets, the maximum input context length is set to 3200 tokens and output to 800 tokens.",
    "Necessary filtering is applied to ensure our datasets fit with this context length limitation.",
    "Each fine-tuning job is conducted with two epochs on the dataset.",
    "Appendix A.3 details other hyperparameters we apply for the fine-tuning process."
  ]
}